2 while loops: one for session, one for game

while session
{ while game
  {
  }
}

switch statement in session: 1 game, 2 HoF, 3 exit
switch statement in game: 1 hit, 2 hold, 3 check, 4 quit

switch in game constantly repeats the game (resetting the deck and hands with each loop)

